Definition: the collection of books of the Gospels, Acts of the Apostles, the Pauline and other epistles, and Revelation
Example: composed soon after Christ's death; the second half of the Christian Bible
Synonyms: Testament, Bible, p, the, collection, of, books, Gospels, Acts, Apostles, Pauline, and, other, epistles, Revelation, composed, soon, after, Christ, s, death, second, half, Christian
Category: noun.communication
